        BASED_ON_THE_EXPANSION_OF_THE_COALITION_IONIS                        = 7436,  -- Based on the expansion of the [Pioneers'/Peacekeepers'/Couriers'/Scouts'/Inventors'/Mummers'] Coalition, Ionis provides[.../ no additional benefits.]
