        THANKS_FOR_COMING_ALL_THIS_WAY_I_D                                   = 7502,  -- Thanks for coming all this way. I'd love to offer you some hospitality, but we'd need to get this frontier station completed first! Could you lend us a hand by signing up for a coalition assignment?
        THANKS_SO_MUCH_FOR_DELIVERING_THIS_I_CAN                             = 7503,  -- Thanks so much for delivering this %! I can't wait to see how this station looks once it's built. If you want, you can go pick up your reward from the manager who gave you this assignment.
        WE_RE_GLAD_YOU_TRIED_YOUR_BEST_BUT                                   = 7504,  -- We're glad you tried your best, but destroyed % are useless to us. Sorry, but can you pick up another one from the manager in charge?
        WELCOME_TO_THE_FRONTIER_THIS_STATION_HAS_ALREADY                     = 7505,  -- Welcome to the frontier! This station has already been built, but you can always help construct some bivouacs or keep them supplied.
        FRONTIER_STATIONS_ARE_SELF_SUFFICIENT_BUT_THE_BIVOUACS               = 7506,  -- Frontier stations are self-sufficient, but the bivouacs are sadly not. We'd be extremely appreciative if you could undertake some assignments to make sure they stay in operation.
        HELLO_THERE_WE_HAVE_SOME_MATERIALS_WE_D                              = 7507,  -- Hello, there! We have some materials we'd like delivered to town, but we have to go through the right channels. Would you mind undertaking a coalition assignment to transport them back?
        THANK_YOU_FOR_HELPING_US_OUT_HERE_S                                  = 7508,  -- Thank you for helping us out. Here's the %. All we ask is that you take it to the manager in charge of this assignment.
        THANK_YOU_FOR_HELPING_US_OUT_ALL_WE                                  = 7509,  -- Thank you for helping us out. All we ask is that you deliver your cargo safely to the manager in charge of this assignment.
        WELL_HERE_S_ANOTHER_BUT_PLEASE_BE_CAREFUL                            = 7510,  -- Well, here's another %, but please be careful not to break this one.
        GOOD_DAY_TO_YOU_THIS_IS_FRONTIER_BIVOUAC                             = 7511,  -- Good day to you. This is [the future site of /]frontier bivouac [#1/#2/#3/#4/#5].
        THANK_YOU_FOR_THE_WE_GREATLY_APPRECIATE_YOUR                         = 7512,  -- Thank you for the %. We greatly appreciate your efforts to [help set up/provision] frontier bivouac [#1/#2/#3/#4/#5]. Please speak with the manager in charge of this assignment to collect your reward.
        I_M_TERRIBLY_SORRY_BUT_WE_CAN_T                                      = 7513,  -- I'm terribly sorry, but we can't use broken %. Could you please return to the coalition assignment desk and procure us another?
        HOW_NICE_IT_IS_TO_SEE_ANOTHER_FACE                                   = 7514,  -- How nice it is to see another face out here! As much as I'd like for you to help us set up frontier bivouac [#1/#2/#3/#4/#5], we won't be able to do anything until we've established a base of operations with a frontier station.
