        IT_S_SO_TOUGH_CONSTRUCTING_FRONTIER_STATIONS_IT                      = 7527,  -- It's so tough constructing frontier stations. It's always build, build, build, and scrounge, scrounge, scrounge. All I want is a little break from the monotony of it all.
